import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1, x2):
    v0 = jnp.add(x1, x2)
    v1 = jnp.minimum(x2, x1)
    v2 = jnp.maximum(v1, v1)
    v3 = jnp.subtract(x2, x1)
    v4 = jnp.minimum(v2, x1)
    v5 = jnp.multiply(v0, v4)
    v6 = jnp.cos(x2)
    v7 = jnp.minimum(v6, x1)
